               <msContents>
                  <summary>Gospel of John, ወንጌል፡ ዘዮሐንስ፡, Horologium of Abba Giyorgis for the night hours, incomplete, ሰዓታት፡ ዘአባ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>

                <msItem xml:id = "p1"><locus from = "1r" to = "2v"/><locus from = "20r" to = "20v"/>
                  <msItem xml:id="p1_i6"><locus from = "20r" to = "20v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2259salota#Isaiah"/><note>Last part only</note></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="p1_i1"><locus target = "#20v #1r" /><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1827Magnif#Mary"/><note><locus target = "#1r"/> continues the prayer starting from <foreign>እስመ፡ ገብረ፡ ሊተ፡ ኃይለ፡ አቢያተ።</foreign></note></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="p1_i2"><locus from = "1v" to = "2r"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2275salota#Zachariah"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="p1_i3"><locus from = "2r" /><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2272salota#Simeon"/><note>One line from the beginning</note></msItem>
                  </msItem>

                <msItem xml:id="p2"><locus from = "3r" to = "17v"/>
                  <msItem xml:id="p2_i4"><locus from = "3r" to = "17v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1693John"/>
                  <note>Arranged for days of the week (Saturday, <locus target = "#12v"/>; Tuesday, <locus target = "#15v"/>)</note>
                  </msItem>
                  </msItem>

                <msItem xml:id="p3"><locus from = "18r" to = "19v"/>
                  <msItem xml:id="p3_i5"><locus from = "18r" to = "19v"/><title type = "complete" ref="LIT3851Hassab"/>
                  <note>Based on the Year 7378 AM (1871 CE)</note>
                  </msItem>
                  </msItem>

                <msItem xml:id="p4"><locus from = "21r" to = "26v"/>
                  <msItem xml:id="p4_i7"><locus from = "21r" to = "26v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1693John"/><note>16th cent</note></msItem>
                  </msItem>

                <msItem xml:id="p5"><locus from = "27r" to = "29v"/>
                  <msItem xml:id="p5_i8"><locus from = "27r" /><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT1864Malkea"/><note>Excerpt from the first part</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                      ኦርኅርኅተ፡ ሕሊና፡ አፍቅሮተ፡ ሰብእ፡ ልማዳ። ሰአሊተ፡ ምሕረት፡ ይእቲ፡ ማርያም፡ ሐፁረ፡ መስቀል፡ ዘየዐውዳ።
                    </incipit>
                    </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="p5_i9"><locus from = "28r" to = "28v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT3056RepCh336"/></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="p5_i10"><locus from = "28v" to = "29v"/><title type = "complete" ref = "LIT2860RepCh141"/><note>Imcomplete at the end</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                      መልክዕ፡ ዘአባ፡ ኪሮስ። አንቅሀኒ፡ እምሃኬትየ፡ ወጸግወኒ፡ ልቡና። ከመ፡ እዜቡ፡ ንስቲተ፡ ለስምከ፡ ውዳሴ፡ ዜና።...
                    </incipit>
                    </msItem>
                    </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="p6"><locus from = "31r" to = "93r"/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i11"><locus from = "31r" to = "34r"/>
                    <title><foreign xml:lang = "gez">አስማት፡</foreign> prayer against charm, <foreign xml:lang = "gez">መፍትሔ፡ ሥራይ፡</foreign></title>
                    <note>Incomplete at the beginning</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                      ከመ፡ [...]ሱ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ወገብርኤል፡ ፍትሑኒ፡ አፍኒን፡ ወራጉኤል፡ ወሳቁኤል፡ ወኵሎሙ፡ መላእክት፡ ሰማያውያን፡ ፍትሑኒ፡ ፬ወንጌላውያን፡ ማቴዎስ፡...
                    </incipit>
                    </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i12">
                    <locus from = "35r" to = "54v"/>
                    <locus from = "55r" to = "58v"/>
                    <locus from = "59v" to = "69v"/>
                    <locus from = "70v" to = "74v"/>
                    <title type = "complete" ref = "LIT3575Mashaf"/>
                    <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                      <note>Lacuna between <locus target = "#54v"/> and <locus target = "#55r"/> and between <locus target = "#74v"/> and <locus target = "#75r"/>; <locus target = "#59r #70r"/> erased; incomplete and rebound in disorder </note>
                      ሰዓታት፡ ዘአባ፡፡ጊዮርጊስ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ አአትብ፡ ወእትነሣእ፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፫አስማተ፡ ነሢእየ፡ እትመረጐዝ፡ እመኒ፡ ወደቁ፡ እትነሣዕ፡..
                    </incipit>
                    </msItem>
                    </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="p7"><locus from = "93r" to = "93v"/>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i13"><locus from = "93r" to = "93v"/>
                    <title><foreign xml:id = "gez">አስማት፡</foreign> prayers against charm, መፍትሔ፡ ሥራይ፡</title>
                    <note><locus target = "#94r"/> erased</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang = "gez">
                      በስመ፡ አብ፡...መፍትሔ፡ ሥራይ፡ ተፈጁን፡ መሐጁን፡ በሀገረ፡ ዳጁን፡ ዘአቅደምኩኩ፡ ወዘፈታሕኩከ፡ ሥራየ፡ ብእሲ፡ ወብእሲት፡ ሥራይ፡ ማሪ፡ ወማሪት፡ ሥራየ፡ ካህናት፡ ወዲያቆናት፡...በስመ፡ አብ፡...መስቀል፡ መግረሬ፡ ፀር፡ ወሰዳዴ፡ አጋንንት፡ አንተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ኩን፡ ጸወነ፡ ናዛዜ፡ ለሕዙናም፡ መጽንኤ፡ ለድኩማን፡...
                    </incipit>
                    </msItem>
                    </msItem>

